content.rendered:
Directed by Trinadha Rao Nakkina.

Written by Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. Trinadha Rao Nakkina. Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. Sai Krishna Biyyapu. Rishabh Purohit.

Cast Nani(Babu). Keerthy Suresh(Keerthi). Naveen Chandra(Siddharth Varma). Sachin Khedekar(Keerthy’s father). Tulasi(Siri). Rao Ramesh(Bride’s father). Krishna Murali Posani(Babu’s father). Raghu Babu(Siddharth’s father). Rajitha(Siddharth’s mother). Vennela Kishore(Store Salesman). Prabhas Sreenu(Nimmakayala Raghu). Krishna Bhagavan(K. Nanchariah). Anish Kuruvilla(College Principal). Viva Raghav(Salesman) .Mahesh Achanta.Karate Kalyani. Easwari Rao(Babu’s mother (as Eshwari Rao)).Pavala Shyamala.Karan Viijay

Language Telugu.

Producers Dil Raju. Harshith Reddy. Sireesh. Bekkam Venugopal.

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations. B2H Studios. Goldmines Telefilms.
